title: Estate Dishwasher Upper Rack Wheel with Mount
description: Estate Dishwasher Upper Rack Wheel with Mount ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 59 Reviews PartSelect Number PS11745451 Manufacturer Part Number WP8268655 This is a replacement upper dish rack wheel with mount for your dishwasher. The mount supports the dish rack, and the wheel allows the rack to slide out easily. To replace this part, remove the rack stops and pull out the upper dish rack. This wheel mount pops off, and the new one can be snapped into place.

installationInstructions.author: James from Gulfport, MS
installationInstructions.title: The wheels on the upper dish rack broke
installationInstructions.content: I removed the end caps on the slides with needle nose pliers, removed the old wheels and installed the new ones, then I snapped the slide end caps back on.  Super responsive service from PartSelect.com Thanks!
